title: Sticky Roast Cauliflower & Beef Fried Rice with Spring Onion & Sesame Seeds
description: Indulge in a symphony of flavors with our sticky roast cauliflower and veggie fried rice. Cauliflower is glazed in a sweet chilli sauce and paired with a veggie-filled and flavourful fried rice for a satisfying and wholesome dining experience.
